title: Emily Ratajkowski flashes her bra in racy sheer lace top | Daily Mail Online
text: Share this article Share Styling her raven tresses in glossy tumbling waves, the Gone Girl actress framed her striking brown eyes with a bronze shimmer. Chic: The model and actress flashed a peek of her bustier bra in a romantic semi-sheer lace top for the glamorous outing after attending Milan Fashion Week Simply stylish: The We Are Your Friends star looked chic in the Victoriana-inspired lace top, which she gave an androgynous edge thanks to some loose-fit boyfriend jeans The relaxed outing comes after private nude snaps of Emily were hacked from her iCloud, according to reports. A link to nearly 200 images of the busty beauty, many of which show her in the buff, were sent to Wayne Rooney prostitute Helen Wood in the hope she'd include them in her column for the Daily Star. The reality personality wrote: 'Last week, I was pondering along through life, when I received a DM on Twitter. No idea who this guy was, but had a peek all the same out of curiosity. Do it in denim: Adding height to her already statuesque frame, the brunette beauty rocked some black ankle-strap courts and carried a leather jacket in her hand Mane attraction: She styled her raven tresses in glossy tumbling waves 'Turns out, it was a link to Emily Ratajkowski's iCloud pictures. This clown had inboxed me and asked that I release the full set of naked images in my column. 'To be clear, this wasn't footage of a randy star salivating at the mouth wanging their bits about while fishing for a random on Skype for a sex sesh. This was private stuff, sent between two people.' Helen explicitly refused to give the images air time and criticised the man who sent them to her. However, a representative for Emily told MailOnline that the images in question were the same ones that were leaked a few years ago.
